name: Jesters of the Cosmic Trip
description: Seemingly appearing out of thin air, the Jesters of the Cosmic Trip aren’t even sure where they themselves are from. Without a known heritage to lean on, they identify as children of the cosmos. They also have a heavy amount of Primordyceps in their diet. Recently they’ve been feeling a little… different. Now residing atop the oasis crabs of Kathoon, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
